{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8109","title":"NG8109: Signals must be invoked in template interpolations.","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8109-signals-must-be-invoked-in-template-interpolations\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3q8x2xaal4zep8x4gaqmndcqx\">NG8109: Signals must be invoked in template interpolations.<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8109#ng8109-signals-must-be-invoked-in-template-interpolations\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8109#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"90dcss8y8j99we1z9ettkcxnz\">Angular 信号是零参数函数（\n<code>() =&gt; T</code>）。执行时，它们返回信号的当前值。 这意味着在模板插值中使用时应该调用它们以渲染其值。</p>\n<h2 id=\"what-should-i-do-instead\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7bicb9bjjdedhs8bfd5vdiby7\">我该怎么办？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8109#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"25bmi8w1wh24us4fcdl91zh4k\">在模板插值中使用信号时，需要调用它以渲染其值。</p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">signal</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  // …\n})\nclass MyComponent {\n    mySignal: <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a><number> = <a href=\"api/core/signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">signal</a>(0)\n}\n</number></code-example>\n<code-example format=\"html\" language=\"html\">\n &lt;div&gt;{{ mySignal() }}/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Signal\n - api/core/signal\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8109#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8109#ng8109-signals-must-be-invoked-in-template-interpolations\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8109#what-should-i-do-instead\n-->"}